gram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Day is a global event that commemorates the birth of the modern Olympic Movement, founded by Pierre de Coubertin in 1894.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999800984071467, \"rank\": 1.9901988867127778e-05, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Day\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"a global event\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"the birth\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's celebration holds special significance as it precedes the highly anticipated Paris 2024 Olympic Games, where Nigerian athletes will compete and inspire the world with their achievements.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9697541604627677, \"rank\": 0.031189182547904242, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This year's celebration\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"special significance\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"the highly anticipated Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"their achievements\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic Day is a chance for people of all ages and abilities to experience the magic of the Olympic Games in their own communities,\\\" said Babatunde Popoola, the Secretary-General of the NOC.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999852481927398, \"rank\": 1.4708038123855124e-05, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic Day\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"all ages\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"abilities\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"the magic\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"their own communities\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"Babatunde Popoola\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"the Secretary-General\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an ideal platform to highlight the benefits of physical activity and the Olympic values of excellence, friendship, and respect.\\\"\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ideal platform\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefits\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"physical activity\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic values\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NOC has received positive responses from various states and stakeholders, and preparations are well underway for the nationwide celebration.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999852481927398, \"rank\": 1.4708038123855124e-05, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"positive responses\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"various states\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"stakeholders\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"the nationwide celebration\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"States such as Abia, Anambra, Bayelsa, Delta, Edo, Enugu, Ebonyi, Lagos, Kogi, Gombe, Jigawa, Kebbi, the Federal Capital Territory, Kano, Kwara, Taraba, Imo, Ondo, Plateau, Rivers, Nasarawa, and Osun have already indicated their plans to organize activities for the event.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayelsa_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.684018549727104e-44, \"text\": \"Bayelsa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayelsa_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bayelsa_State\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ebonyi_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.978119132563627e-65, \"text\": \"Ebonyi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ebonyi_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ebonyi_State\"}, {\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos_State\", \"score\": 0.9999994157098515, \"rank\": 5